{"head":{"description":"custom-property-no-outside-root Deprecated: use the community stylelint-suitcss plugin pack. Disallow custom properties outside of :root…","title":"custom-property-no-outside-root"},"body":"<h1 id=\"custom-property-no-outside-root\"><a href=\"#custom-property-no-outside-root\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>custom-property-no-outside-root</h1>\n<p><strong><em>Deprecated: use the community <a href=\"https://github.com/suitcss/stylelint-suitcss\"><code>stylelint-suitcss</code></a> plugin pack.</em></strong></p>\n<p>Disallow custom properties outside of <code>:root</code> rules.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">    <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">--foo</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span>; }\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/** ↑   ↑\n * These selectors and these types of custom properties */</span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>Options</h2>\n<h3 id=\"true\"><a href=\"#true\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a><code>true</code></h3>\n<p>The following patterns are considered warnings:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">--foo</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span>; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:root</span>, <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">--foo</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span>; }</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are <em>not</em> considered warnings:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-pseudo\">:root</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">--foo</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1px</span>; }</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/custom-property-no-outside-root.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/custom-property-no-outside-root/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/custom-property-no-outside-root/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/custom-property-no-outside-root/index.html.56ac35e40d6333a8a3c3ac7f80fd09b0.json"}